1. install the latest default version of nvidia driver (e.g. v390) from [Software & Updates] in the Ubuntu system
2. download nvidia cuda deb installer
	2.1. sudo dpkg -i cuda-repo-ubuntu1804_10.1.168-1_amd64.deb
	2.2. sudo apt-key adv --fetch-keys https://developer.download.nvidia.com/compute/cuda/repos/ubuntu1804/x86_64/7fa2af80.pub
	2.3. sudo apt-get update
	2.4. sudo apt-get install cuda
3. reboot
4. get into Ubuntu recovery mode -> execute [clean] and [dkpg] function
5. reboot
